\par \loch\af0\dbch\af31505\hich\f0 \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 You hear it here and there, in inns and whorehouses.\'94
\par \loch\af0\dbch\af31505\hich\f0 \'93\loch\f0 Myrish. \hich\f0 \lquote \loch\f0 The Seasons of My Love.\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0  Sweet and sad, if you understand the words. The first girl I ever bedded used to sing i\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 t, and I
