hunt down the men. It was not often outlaws dared prey on travelers so near to Casterly Rock, and he took it as an insult. The girl was too frightened to send off by herself, though, so I offered to take her to the closest inn and feed her while my brothe
\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 r\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0  rode back to the Rock for help.
